    },
    "[aria2](https://aria2.github.io) uses up to 16 connections to download Xcode 3-5x faster than URLSession. Rhodon uses a system-installed aria2c and does not bundle aria2. Install aria2 with Homebrew: brew install aria2. See the [Homebrew formula](https://formulae.brew.sh/formula/aria2).\n\nURLSession is the default Apple API for making URL requests." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the URLSession downloader.",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "[aria2](https://aria2.github.io) uses up to 16 connections to download Xcode 3-5x faster than URLSession. Rhodon uses a system-installed aria2c and does not bundle aria2. Install aria2 with Homebrew: brew install aria2. See the [Homebrew formula](https://formulae.brew.sh/formula/aria2).\n\nURLSession is the default Apple API for making URL requests."
          }
        },
        "ca" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "[aria2](https://aria2.github.io) uses up to 16 connections to download Xcode 3-5x faster than URLSession. Rhodon uses a system-installed aria2c and does not bundle aria2. Install aria2 with Homebrew: brew install aria2. See the [Homebrew formula](https://formulae.brew.sh/formula/aria2).\n\nURLSession is the default Apple API for making URL requests."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "[aria2](https://aria2.github.io) verwendet bis zu 16 Verbindungen, um Xcode 3-5x schneller als URLSession herunterzuladen. Rhodon verwendet ein systemweit installiertes aria2c und bündelt aria2 nicht. Installiere aria2 am besten mit brew install aria2. Siehe auch die [Homebrew-Formel](https://formulae.brew.sh/formula/aria2).\n\nURLSession ist Apples Standard-API für URL-Requests."
          }
        },
